sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Worker
  participant Q as Queue
  participant DB as Metadata DB

  W->>Q: Lease job
  Q-->>W: Job + visibility_timeout
  W->>DB: mark in_progress
  W->>W: Process job
  alt success
    W->>Q: Ack
    W->>DB: mark succeeded
  else failure
    W->>Q: Nack / let timeout expire
    W->>DB: record failure + increment attempts
  end